::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
oregon_counties <-
  counties(state = "OR")
```
:::



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
oregon_counties
```
:::


---


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
oregon_counties |>
  mapview()
```
